elements.name: Login, crear post, publicar post, logout, verificación de post

steps.name: Custom I navigate to page "/ghost"
I enter email "<EMAIL>"
I enter password "<PASSWORD>"
I click sign in
I wait for 1 seconds
I press the labs button
I press the delete all button
I press the confirm delete all button
I press the button close deletion alert
I wait for 1 seconds
Custom I navigate to page "/ghost/#/posts"
I press the create post button
I fill the post title field "¿Cómo ser el mejor Full Stack Developer?"
I fill the post body field "Es bastante probable que con frecuencia encuentres contenido hablando maravillas de un lenguaje en específico."
I press the publish button
I press the button to confirm the publication of a post
I press the button the confirmation modal publish
I wait for 1 seconds
I press the button to return to the post list
I press the button to close the confirmation modal of the publication of a post
